org.irri.iric.portal.dao

Interface ListItemsDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ListItemsDAOImpl

    public interface ListItemsDAO
    Cache frequently used lists of objects, the list is queried from the database on first use. This class is used by the VarietyFacade, GenomicsFacade and GenotypeFacade implementations
    Author:
    LMansueto
